'''艾蜜莉·葛蕾絲·貝文'''（{{lang-en|Emily Grace Bevan}}，{{bd|1982年|8月11日|catIdx=B}}<ref name="dailymail150215">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2950697/Spotlight-Actress-Emily-Bevan.html|title=Spotlight: Actress Emily Bevan shines in a dark J K Rowling tale for grown-ups|publisher=Daily Mail Online|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=7 June 2015|language=en}}</ref><ref name="twitter140811">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DomMitchell/status/4988013182960394243|title=It's the moregous Emily Bevan's birthday today|Author=[[Dominic_Mitchell|Dominic Mitchell]]|publisher=twitter.com|date= 11 August 2014 |accessdate=7 June 2015|language=en}}</ref>），[[英國人|英國]][[女演員|女演員]]， 最為人所熟知的戲劇演出為《[[臨時空缺|臨時空缺]]》<ref name="TCV">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedebrief.co.uk/2015/02/emily-bevan-from-the-casual-vacancy-tells-us-how-it-all-came-together#.VPX-WfmsWN0|title=Emily Bevan From The Casual Vacancy Tells Us How It All Came Together|author=Jess Commons|publisher=The Debrief|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=7 June 2015|language=en}}</ref>與《[[复生_(电视剧)|復生]]》<ref name="ITF">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbcamerica.com/in-the-flesh/extras/interviews/emily-bevan-interview/|title=Exclusive Q&A with ‘In the Flesh’ Actress Emily Bevan|publisher=BBC America|accessdate=7 June 2015|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522225212/http://www.bbcamerica.com/in-the-flesh/extras/interviews/emily-bevan-interview/|archivedate=22 May 2015}}</ref>。

==私生活==
貝文生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[施洛普郡|施洛普郡]][[什魯斯伯里|什魯斯伯里]]，其父為一所男校的[[校長|校長]]，其母則為[[助產士|助產士]]，而她是四個手足中最年幼的<ref name="dailymail150215"/>。她曾就讀於[[中央演講和戲劇學院|中央演講和戲劇學院]]，並在該校取得古典表演（classical acting）的文學碩士學位<ref name="cv">{{cite web|url=http://www.spotlight.com/1530-1203-7853|title=Emily Bevan's CV at Spotlight.com|publisher=Spotlight.com|accessdate=7 June 2015|language=en}}</ref>。

